ach on samples with a wide range\nof in-plane thermal conductivity, including fused silica, rutile titania (TiO2\n[001]), zinc oxide (ZnO [0001]), molybdenum disulfide (MoS2), hexagonal boron\nnitride (h-BN), and highly ordered pyrolytic graphite (HOPG).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Apr 2017 20:05:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-04"}
