erated mainly from dense gas focussed from deeper within the primary-star's\nenvelope. This rapid initial inspiral timescale carries potential implications\nfor the timescale of transients from early common envelope interaction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Apr 2017 20:57:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-19"}
