ent computation of the time-dependent transition probability because\nit allows for pre-computation of time-independent components before the start\nof the calculations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 8 Apr 2017 02:47:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-11"}
