 physics, as well as in\nintroductory classes about the scientific method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 8 Apr 2017 06:24:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Jul 2017 00:53:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-14"}
