h a sensor placed at X{\\deg} = 5 cm was found as the\nbest option for determining both properties with the same experiment. These OED\nparameters have then been used for the determination of moisture permeability\nand advection coefficients. The estimated moisture permeability coefficients\nare twice higher than the a priori values obtained using standard methods. The\nadvection parameter corresponds to the mass average velocity of the order of v\n= 0.01 mm/s within the material and may play an important role on the\nsimulation of moisture front.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 8 Apr 2017 09:37:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 Jul 2017 08:57:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-20"}
